result.name: Paisano's Pizzaria

reviews.text: Great for a quick bite to eat when you don't have time for a proper sit-down meal. As a vegetarian, I think the options were a little limited and also since the pizzas aren't made to order, some ran the risk of being slightly dry. Service was great though!
Fairly decent pizza - for great prices! Definitely worth it if you're craving a big piece of new York style pizza without breaking the bank

Reasonable pizza place for a late night feed conveniently located near the drinking areas. Pizzas are quite big, so a slice would do sufficiently. Not the best quality, but great for soaking up some booze. They also sell beer
Pizza is pretty consistent.  Good value for price point.  Toppings to bread ratio seems to have declined over the years - a result of HK inflation.  Still good for a quick lunch.

This pizza restaurant is a great place to bring your family for a meal. The prices are reasonable, and the pizza sizes are extraordinary. The small size looks like a medium size pizza! I strongly recommend going to this place, as the tastes are amazing, and the staff are always friendly.

result.name: Paisano's

reviews.text: 밤에 갔었는데 생맥기계 근처에 컵위에 막 박귀볼레 돌아다니고요... 거기까진 참았는데 피자에서 샤프심정도 굵기의 철심같은게 나와서 결국 환불받았네요 뭐 철심 발견하기 전까지 조금 먹어본 바로는 맛은 나쁘지 않았지만 위생 최악이라 아무리 맛있어도 먹고싶지 않네요ㅋㅋㅋ 안보는 사이에 피자위에도 박귀볼레가 돌아다니면서 먼저 시식했을지도 모르고요ㅎㅎ

這是一家Pizza 連鎖店，要弄得好吃只需要配芳和時間的設定上，有一套固定的流程，訓練好員工，他們把在工場預先處理好，弄得井井有條，重量和數量計算好，做成一份一份，然後發送到每一家分店，員工打開後，把材料依照之前設定好的流程，分工合作，跟住做可以給客人了，而且pizza內每種東西只要清洗乾淨，肉類沒有發臭，再加上放在高温的爐內，甚麼細菌也沒有生存的空間，那這種食物是不會失敗的。
這家分店也是跟其他的差不多，希望店內餐桌可以常勤清洗乾淨，也是一樣很油，地板不乾淨！
